name: Matt Musgrove
text: When I want a pizza I order from round table. It tastes pretty darn good and is relatively inexpensive. There are cheaper places, but the quality really falls off. I can find a place with better tasting pizza, but it's more expensive than I care for. Round Table fits the bill perfectly.

name: Risa Hernandez
text: They have better hot wings here the Buffalo wild wings! I hope you all will come try them you will be surprised how good they are.

name: Paul Fanning
text: We go fairly often. The food is good. We like it because their ingredients are made fresh every day. We like the Italian Supreme and a few cheese breadsticks. Probably a ton of calories, it is pizza after all, but much more delicious than Dominos.

name: Ray Gonzales State Farm Agent
text: Totally different experience this time around. Even with lots of pizzas being prepared for delivery to NFL playoff households & lots of rain outside, nothing deterred this great crew of providing me EXCELLENT customer service. â€¦More
